author: The Critical Drinker
description:
You know the score - a bunch of people cheat death, and death decides to fight back. But does Bloodlines recapture the old magic of the Final Destination franchise, or is it a lame cash grab rehash? Let's find out. 

Check out our new comic, Saints and Sinners over at Rippaverse: https://rippaverse.com/
title: Final Destination Bloodlines - Its Ridiculous Slop, And I Love It
